        <h2 id="faq">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What is Majestic SEO?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Majestic is a specialised backlink analysis tool founded in 2004. Its Trust Flow and Citation Flow scores are the most respected proprietary link metrics in the industry, backed by a 4.5+ trillion URL Historic Index and a Fresh Index of 227+ billion URLs updated daily.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">How much does Majestic cost in 2026?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Lite $49.99/mo, Pro $99.99/mo, API $399.99/mo. Annual billing saves around 17%. No free trial, but a 7-day money-back guarantee. There is a free Backlink Checker for spot lookups.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What are Trust Flow and Citation Flow?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Citation Flow measures the quantity of links pointing to a page; Trust Flow measures the quality of those sources by their proximity to trusted seed sites. They are Majestic's proprietary alternatives to Moz Domain Authority and Ahrefs Domain Rating.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Does Majestic do keyword research or content?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Majestic is a backlink-only tool. It has no keyword research, no content scoring, no rank tracking, and no site auditing. You need other tools to fill those gaps.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Majestic vs Ahrefs — which has the bigger index?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Ahrefs publishes a larger live index (35T+ links), but Majestic's Historic Index goes back to 2006 and is the only place to find decade-old link data. Ahrefs wins on freshness; Majestic wins on history and Trust Flow as a metric.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Is Majestic worth $49/mo in 2026?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>For link-building specialists, domain brokers, and SEO consultants who need deep historical backlink forensics — yes. For business owners who need content and rankings — no. You will still need writers, an optimiser, and a publishing workflow.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Does Majestic have a free trial?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No standard free trial. There is a 7-day money-back guarantee and a free Backlink Checker for limited spot lookups, but the paid plans require commitment up front.</p></div></div></div>
